779
00:38:00,000 --> 00:38:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Imamo konfor.

780
00:38:01,000 --> 00:38:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Imamo konfor velike, a nismo ono tog svjesni, a možda smo i malo zli.

781
00:38:05,000 --> 00:38:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Onako.

782
00:38:06,000 --> 00:38:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nismo.

783
00:38:07,000 --> 00:38:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nismo.

784
00:38:08,000 --> 00:38:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] Aj ti ovako.

785
00:38:09,000 --> 00:38:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam imam jako puno prijatelja ovdje koje stvarno cijenim i volim.

786
00:38:12,000 --> 00:38:13,000
