787
00:38:13,000 --> 00:38:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kao osjećanku, kažu da kadlučani imaju neka posebna mentalitet, je li to istina?

788
00:38:18,000 --> 00:38:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sad, meni je teško to reći.

789
00:38:20,000 --> 00:38:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja znam da imamo taj govor malo ono...

790
00:38:23,000 --> 00:38:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa mi je osjećani, imamo svoj govor.

791
00:38:26,000 --> 00:38:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Imate lijepu dikciju.

792
00:38:27,000 --> 00:38:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Slovoncima je možda najljepšu ovu dikciju.

793
00:38:29,000 --> 00:38:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znamo zavlačiti dosta.

794
00:38:32,000 --> 00:38:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Malo se meni to pomiješalo i dalje mi se čuje, naravno.

795
00:38:36,000 --> 00:38:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali mi se malo pomiješalo s vašim Karlovačkim sad.

796
00:38:39,000 --> 00:38:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad si naša?

797
00:38:40,000 --> 00:38:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja se osjećam kao Karlovčanka i kad me netko pita odakle sam ja većinom kažem iz Karlovca.

798
00:38:45,000 --> 00:38:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] I onda objasnim da sam doseljenik zapravo.

799
00:38:48,000 --> 00:38:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] A kako, dobro ovisi u dosta. Uči dijelekte.

800
00:38:51,000 --> 00:38:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Imaš ono...

801
00:38:52,000 --> 00:38:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ovisi koliki si sluhista.

802
00:38:54,000 --> 00:38:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da, da.

803
00:38:55,000 --> 00:38:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Recimo, ja nisam baš, ja sam više ovako rada rukama plesa fizičkog.

804
00:38:59,000 --> 00:39:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ti meni više ono konarjnik američke vojske, znaš ono.

805
00:39:02,000 --> 00:39:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da, ovaj.

806
00:39:03,000 --> 00:39:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Malo polajni tu, brže to da ide.

807
00:39:05,000 --> 00:39:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Hitlerovka.

808
00:39:07,000 --> 00:39:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šalim se.

809
00:39:08,000 --> 00:39:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zezom se.

810
00:39:09,000 --> 00:39:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, meni možda teže učiti naglaske.

811
00:39:11,000 --> 00:39:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, sješeš, naučit ćeš, zapamtit ćeš, naćeš si neke mehanizme kako ih zapamtit.

812
00:39:16,000 --> 00:39:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali nisam netko ko će na prvu znati dobro imitirati bilo koje narječe.

813
00:39:21,000 --> 00:39:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, tebe ne smeta ni naša magla, ni naše ova, ni ništa.

814
00:39:26,000 --> 00:39:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nas sve smeta.

815
00:39:28,000 --> 00:39:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne.

816
00:39:29,000 --> 00:39:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Još nemate ni komaraca.

817
00:39:31,000 --> 00:39:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] E, da.

818
00:39:32,000 --> 00:39:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Imamo nešto, ali nisu ko osječki.

819
00:39:34,000 --> 00:39:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo ovako.

820
00:39:35,000 --> 00:39:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jebate, otkutavamo tu komaraca.

821
00:39:37,000 --> 00:39:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Is kopačkog rita.

822
00:39:38,000 --> 00:39:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

823
00:39:39,000 --> 00:39:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Močarno je područje.

824
00:39:40,000 --> 00:39:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, da.

825
00:39:41,000 --> 00:39:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Puno je bara.

826
00:39:42,000 --> 00:39:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

827
00:39:43,000 --> 00:39:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mi imamo jednu baru u centru i na nju smo jako ponosni.

828
00:39:45,000 --> 00:39:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Možemo te poslije ovaj...

829
00:39:47,000 --> 00:39:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Provej se malo da prošetam.

830
00:39:48,000 --> 00:39:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da vidiš.

831
00:39:49,000 --> 00:39:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sve što nisam još upoznal ovih šest godina u Karlo.

832
00:39:52,000 --> 00:39:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kok si šest godina si to?

833
00:39:54,000 --> 00:39:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Šest godina.

834
00:39:55,000 --> 00:39:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] I zavodila si ga više nego mnogi Karlo.

835
00:39:58,000 --> 00:39:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jel, moram.

836
00:39:59,000 --> 00:40:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali sad čuo da imaš tako puno biljaka u stranu, da voliš biljke.

837
00:40:02,000 --> 00:40:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da, sad više ih nemam tako puno kao što sam ih imala.

838
00:40:05,000 --> 00:40:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer nemaš veliki stran?

839
00:40:06,000 --> 00:40:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne.

840
00:40:07,000 --> 00:40:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nego sam se previše zaposlila i onda se ne stignem brinuti.

841
00:40:10,000 --> 00:40:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pa sam dio razdijelila, dio je nažalost pokojan.

842
00:40:14,000 --> 00:40:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali da, imam ih sigurno šest desetak.

843
00:40:18,000 --> 00:40:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer to zbog kosika, izelenila ili ono?

844
00:40:21,000 --> 00:40:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] I volim prirodu, volim biljke i mislim da je prostor u kojemu su biljke puno topliji.

845
00:40:26,000 --> 00:40:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da, je.

846
00:40:27,000 --> 00:40:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ne znam, ja kad sam, ako se ne osjećam možda dobro ako sam nervozna ali nešto, uzmem biljku pre sadica, ali to brisat listiće, to me jako smiruje.

847
00:40:36,000 --> 00:40:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je neka vrsta meditacije.

848
00:40:38,000 --> 00:40:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da, kone, bonsai, kak zove?

849
00:40:39,000 --> 00:40:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da, bonsai, kad ga režu, da.

850
00:40:41,000 --> 00:40:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] To ne znam da bi imala dovoljno živaca.

851
00:40:43,000 --> 00:40:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da, me je to interesiralo, nisam se nikad odlučio.

852
00:40:45,000 --> 00:40:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Možda dođe vrijeme kad...

853
00:40:47,000 --> 00:40:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da, volim biljke.

854
00:40:48,000 --> 00:40:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tek mi je 29 godina, ali mi imamo vremen na...

855
00:40:50,000 --> 00:40:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] A smijem ja reklamirati ovdje?

856
00:40:52,000 --> 00:40:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno.

857
00:40:53,000 --> 00:40:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Izvrsno.

858
00:40:54,000 --> 00:40:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kolegica i ja smo htjeli pokrenuti svoj biznis s kaktusima.

859
00:40:58,000 --> 00:41:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Trebala sam izrađivati tegle, odnosno posude, zajedno zgaditi kaktuse i onda pokrenuti biznis.

860
00:41:07,000 --> 00:41:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nažalost, ja sam se previše zaposlila i nekako...

861
00:41:11,000 --> 00:41:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Je to palo u drugi plan kod mene, ali ona je počela, lagano sad otvara svoj obrt.

862
00:41:17,000 --> 00:41:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] Slobodno.

863
00:41:18,000 --> 00:41:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Zove se kaktus Sandra.

864
00:41:20,000 --> 00:41:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Možete joj naći na Instagramu.

865
00:41:22,000 --> 00:41:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Radi stvarno super stvari.

866
00:41:24,000 --> 00:41:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] To iz Karlovca.

867
00:41:25,000 --> 00:41:26,000
[SPEAKER_00] Top iz Karlovca je, da.

868
00:41:26,000 --> 00:41:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja imam dobru frendicu koja voli kaktuse, ali svake ju gine.

869
00:41:30,000 --> 00:41:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Eto.

870
00:41:31,000 --> 00:41:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali misli da je problem u frendici.

871
00:41:33,000 --> 00:41:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Znaju se kupiti i bolesne kaktuse, tako da možda nije samo u frendici.

